If there is invalid branch syntax in the Pipelines YML, it won&#x27;t detect the syntax as invalid and allow you to attempt a build. The problem is that the build will never trigger, and you&#x27;re stuck with an indefinite spinner

For example:

{code}
#!python

pipelines:
  branches:
    &#x27;{bug-**,feat-**,master}&#x27;:
{code}

